languages.text: "Я слышу в твоем голосе... понимание? Ясно. Ты тоже совершила ошибку, достойную гибели — и избежала ее".
"I hear... understanding in your voice? I see. You, too, made a mistake that should have spelt your doom — and escaped it."

languages.text: “我听到……你的声音里包含着理解的意味？我明白了。你和我一样，也犯下了足以致死的大错，但你也同样逃过了一劫。”
languages.original_text: "I hear... understanding in your voice? I see. You, too, made a mistake that should have spelt your doom — and escaped it."

languages.text: « Serait-ce... de la compréhension que je perçois dans votre voix ? Je crois comprendre. Vous avez vous aussi commis une erreur qui aurait dû vous coûter la vie, mais vous en avez réchappé. »
languages.original_text: "I hear... understanding in your voice? I see. You, too, made a mistake that should have spelt your doom — and escaped it."

traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: «¿Es... comprensión lo que oigo en tu voz? Ya veo. Tú también cometiste un error que debería haberte costado la vida... y sobreviviste».
languages.original_text: "I hear... understanding in your voice? I see. You, too, made a mistake that should have spelt your doom — and escaped it."

languages.text: 「それは…理解しているように聞こえるが？そうか、あなたもその生が終わるかもしれない過ちを犯し…その運命から逃れたのだな」
languages.original_text: "I hear... understanding in your voice? I see. You, too, made a mistake that should have spelt your doom — and escaped it."

languages.text: "Ich höre ... Verständnis in Eurer Stimme? Ich verstehe. Auch Ihr habt einen Fehler begangen, der Euren Untergang hätte bedeuten sollen — und seid entkommen."
